                 ARE YOU A PATHWAY CONNECT GRADUATE?
                </h2>
                <p>
                 Great news! LDSBC is now offering the Pathway Scholarship to ALL students who complete the Pathway Program in the United States with a 3.0 GPA or higher. Making it more affordable than ever to get the skills you need for a satisfying career.
                </p>
