            <div class="module steps-with-links-block ">
             <div class="module-container">
              <h3 class="swlb-title">
               You're Ready To Enroll. Start Here.
              </h3>
              <div class="swlb-content">
               <div>
                <div>
                 <div class="module step">
                  <div class="s-number">
                  </div>
                  <div class="vc">
                   <h4 class="s-title">
                    Apply online.
                   </h4>
                   <p class="s-description">
                    Simply visit apply.lds.org. Then click “Apply Here &amp; Check Application Status” to begin your application status and create your Net ID.
                   </p>
                  </div>
                 </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                 <div class="module step">
                  <div class="s-number">
                  </div>
                  <div class="vc">
                   <h4 class="s-title">
                    Transcripts and endorsement.
                   </h4>
                   <p class="s-description">
                    During the application process, send in any relevant past transcripts. And don’t forget. You’ll also need to receive an ecclesiastical endorsement from your religious leader.
                   </p>
                  </div>
                 </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                 <div class="module step">
                  <div class="s-number">
                  </div>
                  <div class="vc">
                   <h4 class="s-title">
                    Acceptance.
                   </h4>
                   <p class="s-description">
                    After your application process is complete, our admissions department will review your application. When we make an admissions decision, we’ll notify you by email.
                   </p>
                  </div>
                 </div>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
