                  <div class="testimonial-testimonial">
                   When friends suggested I look into LDS Business College, I dropped my scholarship and transferred there. I don't regret it. I have felt so welcome, and I feel blessed by the school honor code and how we invite the Spirit every time we study.
                  </div>
                  <div class="testimonial-name">
                   Dora Situmorang, Accounting
